/* 首页 = 清新浅色 + 薄荷青（令牌真源见 app.wxss）：大卡、真实数据、克制留白。 */
.squad {
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: var(--bg);
  padding: 0 32rpx calc(env(safe-area-inset-bottom) + 180rpx);
}

.sq-top { padding: 36rpx 8rpx 28rpx; }
.sq-eyebrow { font-size: 26rpx; color: var(--sub); }
.sq-h1 { margin-top: 8rpx; font-size: 52rpx; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -1rpx; }

.card-press { transform: scale(0.99); }

/* ===== AI 名片大卡 ===== */
.hero {
  padding: 40rpx 36rpx 8rpx;
  border-radius: var(--r-3xl); margin-bottom: 20rpx;
  background: var(--surface); border: 1rpx solid var(--border); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift);
}
.hero-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28rpx; }
.hero-av {
  position: relative; flex: 0 0 auto; width: 120rpx; height: 120rpx; border-radius: 32rpx;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1fc49c, var(--accent-strong));
  font-size: 50rpx; font-weight: 500; color: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 6rpx 18rpx rgba(24, 182, 144, 0.22);
}
.hero-dot { position: absolute; right: -4rpx; bottom: -4rpx; width: 28rpx; height: 28rpx; border-radius: 50%; background: #34d399; border: 6rpx solid var(--surface); }
.hero-id { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.hero-name { font-size: 38rpx; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.5rpx; }
.hero-line { margin-top: 10rpx; font-size: 27rpx; color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.5; }
.hero-go { flex: 0 0 auto; font-size: 34rpx; color: var(--faint); }

.hero-stats {
  display: flex; margin-top: 32rpx; padding: 28rpx 0 24rpx;
  border-top: 1rpx solid var(--line);
}
.hstat { flex: 1; text-align: center; position: relative; }
.hstat::after { content: ''; position: absolute; right: 0; top: 12rpx; bottom: 12rpx; width: 1rpx; background: var(--line); }
.hstat:last-child::after { display: none; }
.hstat-n { font-size: 44rpx; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.5rpx; }
.hstat-l { margin-top: 6rpx; font-size: 23rpx; color: var(--faint); }

/* 谁看过我 */
.seen {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12rpx;
  padding: 26rpx 32rpx; border-radius: 28rpx; margin-bottom: 32rpx;
  background: var(--accent-soft); font-size: 27rpx; color: var(--accent-deep);
  transition: background 0.16s var(--ease);
}
.seen-press { background: #ddf0e7; }
.seen-ic { font-size: 32rpx; color: var(--accent); }
.seen text { flex: 1; }
.seen-go { font-size: 30rpx; color: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.4); }

/* 区段标 */
.sec-label { padding: 0 8rpx 18rpx; font-size: 24rpx; letter-spacing: 3rpx; color: var(--faint); }

/* ===== Agent 大卡 ===== */
.acard {
  padding: 32rpx 32rpx 24rpx; border-radius: var(--r-2xl); margin-bottom: 22rpx;
  background: var(--surface); border: 1rpx solid var(--border); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
}
.acard-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 26rpx; }
.acard-ic {
  flex: 0 0 auto; width: 100rpx; height: 100rpx; border-radius: 28rpx;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--accent-soft);
}
.acard-ic text { font-size: 42rpx; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent-deep); }
.acard-meta { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.acard-name { font-size: 32rpx; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
.acard-tag { margin-top: 8rpx; font-size: 26rpx; color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.5; }
.acard-foot {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  margin-top: 26rpx; padding-top: 22rpx; border-top: 1rpx solid var(--line);
}
.acard-pill { font-size: 23rpx; padding: 8rpx 22rpx; border-radius: var(--r-full); background: var(--accent-soft); color: var(--accent-ink); }
.acard-cta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6rpx; font-size: 26rpx; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent-strong); }
.acard-cta-ic { font-size: 26rpx; }
